00:11:30.900 --> 00:11:32.310
Oh non!

00:11:33.120 --> 00:11:35.010
Ça y est!

00:11:35.010 --> 00:11:37.110
Qu-Que s'est-il passé ?

00:11:37.110 --> 00:11:39.940
Luffy-sama.

00:11:39.940 --> 00:11:41.480
Je suis désolé.

00:11:41.480 --> 00:11:44.850
Yowahoshi !

00:11:44.850 --> 00:11:50.290
